{"tid":2183572,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"臺灣家居檢疫實況分享","createTime":"2020-09-01T04:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T17:30:17.000Z","uid":180602,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9561ca7461b19bbaf7a8b43246d21e6211a69d28","tid":2183572,"uid":180602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:20:32.000Z","msg":"喺隔離台見到有巴打出po分享頹飯，覺得幾有趣，加上太無聊，所以決定照板煮碗<br />\n<br />\n基於「食得是福」、「有食唔食罪大惡極」，一般情況下放得落口就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay1<br />\n<strong>早餐: 白粥配肉鬆、鹹蛋、荀......</strong><br />\n白粥就咁食無比較淡，加D肉鬆同荀送會易入味啲<br />\n鹹蛋就普普通通<br />\n菜同麵筋就...你鍾意食會覺得好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bzLsTnM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbzLsTnM.jpg&h=7cc98045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>午餐: 雞扒意粉 (少量肉醬底)、粟米羹</strong><br />\n意粉味道還好，但太多油，加上塊雞扒疑似炸過嚟，頂唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n粟米羹就普普通通<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/esRf2f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FesRf2f5.jpg&h=bc8d2a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>晚餐: 普通自助餐(?) 配橙一個同涼粉一碗</strong><br />\n啲鮮魷幾好食，欖菜肉粒 (唔肯定)都還好，係油咗啲，其他就普普通通，正常臺灣水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過個橙零舍「開胃」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/372ZKut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F372ZKut.jpg&h=6e74f65c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba9c5330bdb0d1f039d17a5ad0ff43cfb67c7de3","tid":2183572,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:21:22.000Z","msg":"睇落幾正"},{"pid":"d232497550926062108b2f94042e39092bc09a15","tid":2183572,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daddf934bc3bd34b37cba0fd23b5d36394f368e3","tid":2183572,"uid":302656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"Lm 巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582ed1af95a7c6ab97406379b27761c05392d614","tid":2183572,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:22:55.000Z","msg":"點解隔離都可以食得咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0db7731fb191b13aee8458cb1680efadc57d47","tid":2183572,"uid":87820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"好食過平時打工仔既LUNCH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a182b3a893a7582c2675cd2a728ba30f759fd060","tid":2183572,"uid":9672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"邊度？台中？"},{"pid":"95be9b82f732dfeade4d5ada46a124e6465188c3","tid":2183572,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/372ZKut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F372ZKut.jpg&h=6e74f65c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n為了你的健康,隔餐請勿食用<br />\n咩意思呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9595f0e6a2a5e4204c9eb39af8f385622074dff1","tid":2183572,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95be9b82f732dfeade4d5ada46a124e6465188c3","tid":2183572,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/372ZKut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%