src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:43:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會係早餐唔好留到中午食咁呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:54:10.000Z","msg":"YES<br />\n俗啲講就係快撚啲食啦擺吓擺吓變壞咗食到肚痛唔好話我冇警告你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真香港買飯盒你都唔會擺幾個鐘然後先食㗎啦<br />\n同一道理啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:29:57.000Z","msg":"咁又係嘅...<br />\n家居檢疫得三樣嘢好做啫...<br />\n食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗同佢慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e317eb7809e739368c60ba9fb88417a38338ec2","tid":2183572,"uid":180602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T11:00:12.000Z","msg":"第二日<br />\n<br />\n<strong>早餐: 西式</strong><br />\n普通早餐，不過個包入面搽嘅係蒜蓉醬而唔係牛油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而果兩舊薯仔加上迷迭香就變得麻麻地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0vQAj4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0vQAj4H.jpg&h=1b015f46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>午餐: 中式粥加點心(?)</strong><br />\n今次真係打大佬，首先啲粥加咗啲小米 (黃色果啲) 落去好奇怪<br />\n然後個奶黃包同個蛋糕都太甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住就係果兩舊糯米原來係包住舊豬肉球，真係估佢唔倒<br />\n最後就係啡色果兜，<br />\n本身以為係醬油膏之類嘅調味料，點知原來係咖啡凍 (唔知佢叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HEATRbp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHEATRbp.jpg&h=87794459&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong>晚餐: 雞肉飯配三色蒸蛋，另有貢丸湯同楊桃</strong><br />\n今次個飯幾好食，唔油、唔鹹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tpo98X3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTpo98X3.jpg&h=61e07f06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b6f33346572c755e7854d8c2491daf2123f781f","tid":2183572,"uid":180602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a182b3a893a7582c2675cd2a728ba30f759fd060","tid":2183572,"uid":9672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"邊度？台中？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a67f0ccc7b4107742d4f38f2564d40e80dd283","tid":2183572,"uid":180602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daddf934bc3bd34b37cba0fd23b5d36394f368e3","tid":2183572,"uid":302656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"Lm 巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T11:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f21a74a14740196ff9a82d92c1796771e3be2de","tid":2183572,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8d9e5d38d069640d0a9a28e2df5f42744df61a","tid":2183572,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:13:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c00a4a3f26d387abf384cb2d3747d12896b61868","tid":2183572,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T19:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1c64efc416162fb70bbefa6501fbbb39ea41ce","tid":2183572,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T20:32:16.000Z","msg":"啲飯係有特定機構送餐過嚟定附近叫外賣?"},{"pid":"6a8d8ca9fd7d0eac6bcd8040bdde152f4388e37f","tid":2183572,"uid":180602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f8d9e5d38d069640d0a9a28e2df5f42744df61a","tid":2183572,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202